A site which allows you to find a bitcoin to cash dealer near you, or list your own advertisement and make money by running your own cash exchange. It also allows online transactions and offers escrow and other security services, as well as a reputation system.

The site boasts with exchangers [from 142 countries](https://localbitcoins.com/statistics) and 1733 cities.



